{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a rocky beach scene under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds. A lone figure, a person wearing a dark jacket and shorts, stands on the sandy beach amidst a collection of large, moss-covered rocks. The rocks are varied in size and shape, some forming small pools of water reflecting the sky. The tide appears to be receding, revealing more of the beach and wet sand. Further out, in the distance, more rocky formations emerge from the ocean, suggesting a rugged coastline. The overall scene evokes a sense of remote natural beauty and tranquility. The sand is a light tan color, and the vegetation on the rocks adds patches of green and brown to the landscape.",
